    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Brassieres in the form of a narrow band of fabric worn tightly around the bust, usually without shoulder straps; the term may refer to any women's strapless top in a similar style.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>布製的窄帶形胸罩，緊裹住胸部，通常沒有肩帶；本詞彙可能指任何風格相似的女用無肩帶上衣。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
